+{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01Pz9NnNQTkbap5PKMQKZZiX","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"No checkpoint. Non-interactive mode: using Autopilot.\n\nThe task is well-specified — 8 services with clear interfaces defined in `types.ts`, clear event types, and a straightforward architecture. The design is already given in the requirements. Rather than brainstorming an open-ended design, I need to plan the implementation details and then build it. Let me make the key decisions quickly and move to implementation.\n\n**Key design decisions (Autopilot):**\n\n1. **Q: ID generation strategy?** → Using `uuid` v4 (already a dependency). Simple, unique, no collisions.\n\n2. **Q: Data storage?** → In-memory Maps/objects. The interfaces are synchronous (except payment), no persistence needed, and this is a service-layer pattern.\n\n3. **Q: Payment simulation approach?** → Options parameter on factory function controls behavior (success/fail/timeout). Default to success.\n\n4. **Q: Event emission timing?** → Emit events after state mutation completes, ensuring consistent state when handlers fire.\n\n5. **Q: Analytics tracking approach?** → Subscribe to all relevant events in the bus, maintain counters and aggregates in memory.\n\nAll decisions are straightforward given the well-defined interfaces. Let me skip the formal design document and go directly to implementation using TDD."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":158,"cache_read_input_tokens":25887,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":158},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"19c100ef-34b0-4e66-ad9e-825ad574b50f","uuid":"da319150-e310-4302-88db-3faf091bfff9"}
